Express :- It is a Node.js web application framework that helps in creating web aplications.It is used for server side programming(backend).
Our frontend code works like a client it sends requests to server side and we will build this server side(backend) with help of express.
What express do:-
Express listen for incoming responses.
It parses data(mean it can receives data in any form but it will convert this data into js form )
Matches response with routes(from which side request has came).
Send suitable response according to given request.

Express is a framework but basically its a package in npm and we can install it through npm and this package contain diffrent tools and utilities which help us in server side programming.